RXE 1
ID app-number-spark
NAME Number Spark
ICON N
LAYOUT terminal
COLOR 0xFFF2B84B
INPUT Number:
BUTTON Spark
USE APPKIT
UI PANEL 0 0 230 36 Number Spark
UI BUTTON 8 8 74 20 Spark | 9
UI BADGE 126 9 86 18 C app
UI INPUT 0 46 230 24 Number:
UI OUTPUT 0 84 0 0 Result
DESKTOP 1
DOCK 1
TEXT Type a number. The app runs C-style code stored inside this RXE file.
LANG C
CODE int doubled = input * 2;
CODE println(doubled + 7);
CODE appkit("UI PROGRESS 238 46 150 18 spark | 70");
